Xerox Corp's U.K. unit, Rank XeroxLtd, said it agreed in principle to sell its South Africancompany, Rank Xerox South Africa Pty Ltd, to &lt;Altron Group's>Fintech unit.    Terms of the deal were not disclosed.    Altron said the acquisition was key to making Fintech anoffice systems company.    The South African Rank Xerox unit sells copiers andduplicators throughout South Africa and in Namibia (South WestAfrica). It has over 800 employees, all of whom will beretained by Fintech when the deal closes, Rank Xerox said. Reuter&#3;